data.title: Improve app UI subsystem initialization and project theming support
Jme atomic miscfixes
Support constructor arguments to JSComponent derived components, whil…
Don't x scroll on inspector frame
Inspector Field Improvements
Rake windows build uses global CMAKE_DEV_BUILD var
data.body: I got this up just a moment too late for your previous landing :) Using this var works our side running the rake for distribution builds.

data.title: If JSComponent has a parameter in constructor, it breaks everything
Support enum style choices for inspector fields (like with sprite blending modes, light types, etc)
Fix moving nodes around in the hierarchy frame
Documentation Rain Catch - Important things to document
data.body:
Component inspector fields are valid as of the start function, they are not valid in the constructor as the object has not been created (so the fields couldn't have been set)

An object literal initializer passed to createJSComponent is also valid as of the start function

data.title: When modifying a prefab node in the scene, prompt user to break the prefab or save
data.body: Changes to a prefab will not be stored unless the prefab is either broken or saved

data.title: Added UInt where it needs in Haxe definitions. Removed duplicate
Just some fix in comments, to parse Atomic.js in jsdoc correctly.
Fixed #168
Optimize node transform access from script, by storing a cached array that is returned
data.body: .. instead of generating a new one

data.title: Add an Atomic specific Rakefile for generating full editor builds
data.body: The Rakefile in root should be kept really simple for generating a working AtomicEditor as an example.  There needs to be a mechanism for generating full editor builds, with examples, docs, etc
